1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T09:35:00.000Z","msg":"巴打你好似柒啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家有咩感想"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T09:39:27.000Z","msg":"無 想跳ifc"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T10:34:07.000Z","msg":"當年點解夠膽入AMD?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T10:36:37.000Z","msg":"第一部砌既2機係amd 覺得ok"},{"pid":"c928dc91c3b43a3e96e25046066d91d7a2d16104","tid":2308980,"uid":280593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a0bc72f9b2929b2dcae63b4ab49e9a255d99091","tid":2308980,"uid":40121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T08:46:53.000Z","msg":"無人講就我講啦⋯⋯<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2020年7月13日，巿場仍然一片頽垣敗瓦，係一片恐慌之中，我以每股<span class=\"red\">$22.55</span>嘅價錢買入希慎興業（14），當時股息率係<span class=\"green\">6.4%</span>。買入原因好簡單：<span class=\"gold\"><strong><ins>希慎=軒尼詩道以南大半個銅鑼灣</ins></strong></span>。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TaUbhBz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTaUbhBz.png&h=66451b23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n買完梗係去巡舖啦（其實係路過），果陣啲人（包括我）都仲係好驚武肺，結果我行到銅鑼灣係咁（示意圖咋唔係真係咁的）：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MhHwhBP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMhHwhBP.jpg&h=710920fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n喂屌你⋯⋯無人嘅？條街無人行，商場無人行，啲舖直頭唔撚開，再咁落去啲舖執尻哂咪聽收皮？仲有果啲利園幾期幾期，其實平時都無咩人行過去架喎，自由行又唔落尼買包包⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n總之我果下<span class=\"red\">好驚</span>啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，擺左幾日上上落落，去到<span class=\"limegreen\">24.5</span>就走左嚕（貼倉先）。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zySzZQg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzySzZQg.png&h=6b43cbe9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n時間Fast Forward到今日，武肺just a flu，個撚個中左都無病癥，銅鑼灣變成咁（示意圖again）：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yEdfKg6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyEdfKg6.jpg&h=3fea9ba9&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而希慎興業（14）變成咁： <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mLubhCi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmLubhCi.png&h=6ae9722f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我變成咁：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6QJ0aXp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6QJ0aXp.jpg&h=7b775c13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n比一分鐘大家恥笑下我：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Kofefpd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKofefpd.jpg&h=ecab9d9e&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T10:37:13.000Z","msg":"如果你出左希慎即入ZM AMZN SHOP 賺到你笑"},{"pid":"db10503e82f33df900a82d4eef9b6ad58958ad01","tid":2308980,"uid":131323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T10:54:22.000Z","msg":"買qq賺500蚊走左<br />\n3xx果陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09b9e9c0a45c650b253f3772b67dcde01dd4ed85","tid":2308980,"uid":65928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T11:08:49.000Z","msg":"6.8賣左swire-b<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93ffec29f2c907d4ee52290e548c60bbe05b63c3","tid":2308980,"uid":65928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"54bc363642dd54bd6b366fbcbd2f4b72dba2b27b","tid":2308980,"uid":141060,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"f01fa90d025eca80837555743531e48dcc81d41c","tid":2308980,"uid":40121,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T09:08:42.000Z","msg":"巴絲打們有無啲類似嘅柒野可以分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可摸耳靜靜地留cm等我知唔係得我一個咁柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"